Interface EventProcessor

All Known Subinterfaces:
BackfillingEventProcessor
All Known Implementing Classes:
DeduplicateMultithreadedEventProcessor, DuplicateEventDetectionEventProcessor, MainEventProcessor
public interface EventProcessor
An Event Processor that may mutate or drop an event. Runs for SentryEvent or SentryTransaction

    • getOrder

      @Nullable default @Nullable Long getOrder()
      Controls when this EventProcessor is invoked.
      Returns:
      order higher number = later, lower number = earlier (negative values may also be passed), null = latest (note: multiple event processors using null may lead to random ordering)
